          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（四龙套、四下手、陈泰、司马师同上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "司马师",
          "line_type": "念",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "蜀兵杀法多英勇，我兵退败在铁笼。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（四龙套、郭淮同上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "郭淮",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "参见都督。"
        },
        {
          "character": "司马师",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "将军少礼，请坐。"
        },
        {
          "character": "郭淮",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "谢座。"
        },
        {
          "character": "司马师",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "姜维如此雄猛，我兵只得在此安营，稍避其锋，再作道理。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（内喊声。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "司马师",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "营外何事喧哗？"
        },
        {
          "character": "陈泰",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "待末将前去看来。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（陈泰下。内喊声。陈泰上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "陈泰",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "启都督：不料此山荒僻，山内无水，故而众将士喧哗。"
        },
        {
          "character": "司马师",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "嗳呀不好了。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（〖牌子〗。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "司马师",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "想这营中无水，三军不战自乱，这便如何是好？"
        },
        {
          "character": "郭淮",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "启都督：想昔年诸葛亮征剿南蛮，七擒孟获之时，也是军中无水。那孔明上山"
        },
        {
          "character": "郭淮",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "祈祷，山泉暴出。都督何不也上山祈告上苍，或者天赐泉水，也未可知。"
        },
        {
          "character": "司马师",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "好，山头去者。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（〖牌子〗。众人同转场。场上设香案。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "司马师",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "弟子魏国都督司马师，祷告皇天上帝、济渎等神：今日带兵与蜀兵交战，败至"
        },
        {
          "character": "司马师",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "此山，不想此山无水，三军大乱，叩求上苍，赐下甘泉，以救生命。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（〖牌子〗。场上撤香案。探子上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "探子",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "启都督：山下泉水涌出。"
        },
        {
          "character": "司马师",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "再探。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（探子下。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "司马师",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "天赐甘泉，我等保有生命，我等往空一拜。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（〖牌子〗。探子上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "探子",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "今有姜维，借得西羌十万蛮兵，前来助战。"
        },
        {
          "character": "司马师",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "再探。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（探子下。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "司马师",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "呀。郭将军，今有姜维借得蛮兵助战，如何是好。"
        },
        {
          "character": "陈泰",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "启都督：想那西羌国王迷当，与末将有一面之缘，末将愿去，顺说与他，叫他"
        },
        {
          "character": "陈泰",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "将兵马借与我国，不知都督意下如何？"
        },
        {
          "character": "司马师",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "只怕他未必肯弃姜维，来助我国。"
        },
        {
          "character": "陈泰",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "那迷当为人，喜怒无常，待末将前去搬动是非，借得兵来，也未可知。"
        },
        {
          "character": "司马师",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "就命将军前去，须要小心。"
        },
        {
          "character": "陈泰",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "得令。"
        },
        {
          "character": "陈泰",
          "line_type": "念",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "但凭三寸舌，要借十万兵。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（陈泰下。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "司马师",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "陈泰此去借兵，若得成功，此乃是天助我也。正是："
        },
        {
          "character": "司马师",
          "line_type": "念",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "暗地设下反间计，要与姜维见高低。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（司马师、郭淮、四龙套同下。）"
        }
      ],
      "interactions": [
        {
          "edge": "司马师→郭淮",
