    {
      "scene_index": 4,
      "label": "第四场",
      "characters_present": [
        "四将",
        "四蛮婆",
        "迷当",
        "陈泰"
      ],
      "lines": [
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（四上手、四蛮婆、四将、迷当同上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "迷当",
          "line_type": "点绛唇",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "坐镇西羌，统领儿郎，英雄将，威震四方，无人敢抵挡。"
        },
        {
          "character": "迷当",
          "line_type": "念",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "三国纷纷起战争，孔明火烧藤甲军兵。七擒孟获某在内，陈泰领兵到如今。"
        },
        {
          "character": "迷当",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "孤，迷当。镇守西羌，只因姜维命人前来借兵，是孤未即应允，今特带领蛮兵"
        },
        {
          "character": "迷当",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "番将，迎上前去，看那姜维是怎样行事。"
        },
        {
          "character": "迷当",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "孩子们！"
        },
        {
          "character": "四蛮婆、四将",
          "line_type": "同白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "有。"
        },
        {
          "character": "迷当",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "起兵前往。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（众人同转场。陈泰上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "陈泰",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "参见老大王。"
        },
        {
          "character": "迷当",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "我当是谁，原来是陈将军，前来作甚？"
        },
        {
          "character": "陈泰",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "今奉我都督之令，特与老大王借兵。"
        },
        {
          "character": "迷当",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "陈将军，你来晚啦。我的兵，已经尽借与姜维了。"
        },
        {
          "character": "陈泰",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "呀，老大王，那姜维在背地，曾经辱骂大王，为何借兵与他？"
        },
        {
          "character": "迷当",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "原来如此，那姜维胆敢无礼。孤就将兵马，借与你家就是。"
        },
        {
          "character": "陈泰",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "如此多谢老大王。"
        },
        {
          "character": "迷当",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "孤虽将兵马借与你国，但是一件。"
        },
        {
          "character": "陈泰",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "哪一件。"
        },
        {
          "character": "迷当",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "阵前交战，伤孤一卒……"
        },
        {
          "character": "陈泰",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "赔将一员。"
        },
        {
          "character": "迷当",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "伤孤一骑……"
        },
        {
          "character": "陈泰",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "赔银十两。"
        },
        {
          "character": "迷当",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "君子一言……"
        },
        {
          "character": "陈泰",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "岂能反悔。"
        },
        {
          "character": "迷当",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "好。陈将军先回，孤家大兵，随后就到。"
        },
        {
          "character": "陈泰",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "多谢老大王。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（陈泰下。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "迷当",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "孩子们兵发魏营。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（众人同下。）"
        }
      ],
      "interactions": [
        {
          "edge": "四将→迷当",
          "turns": 1
        },
        {
          "edge": "迷当→陈泰",
