    {
      "scene_index": 5,
      "label": "第五场",
      "characters_present": [
        "夏侯霸",
        "姜维",
        "迷当",
        "马岱"
      ],
      "lines": [
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（姜维上，起霸。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "姜维",
          "line_type": "念",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "小小一计非等闲，司马被困铁笼间。幼习黄公三略法，姜维曾受武侯传。"
        },
        {
          "character": "姜维",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "吾，姓姜名维，字伯约。今奉幼主之命，带领四十五万铁甲雄兵，扫荡中原，"
        },
        {
          "character": "姜维",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "司马师被某一战，被困在铁笼山。昨夜夜观天象，见将星混乱，今日难免一场"
        },
        {
          "character": "姜维",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "鏖战。"
        },
        {
          "character": "姜维",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "马岱、夏侯霸听令。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（马岱、夏侯霸同上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "马岱、夏侯霸",
          "line_type": "同念",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "谯楼鼓打三更尽，夜宿貔貅百万兵。"
        },
        {
          "character": "姜维",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "命你等，各带三千人马，埋伏在铁笼山口，司马师到来，接杀一阵。"
        },
        {
          "character": "马岱、夏侯霸",
          "line_type": "同白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "得令。"
        },
        {
          "character": "马岱、夏侯霸",
          "line_type": "同念",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "计谋安排定，尽在一战中。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（马岱、夏侯霸同下。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "姜维",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "苍天呀，苍天！"
        },
        {
          "character": "姜维",
          "line_type": "念",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "若助弟子三分力，管取中原一战成。"
        },
        {
          "character": "姜维",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "众将官，你等三更时分，饱餐战饭，整顿貔貅，个个奋勇当先，随我出阵。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（四上手、四蛮婆、四将、迷当同上，对阵。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "姜维",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "原来是老大王，姜维马上不能全礼，请了。"
        },
        {
          "character": "迷当",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "姜维你下得马来，孤家有话对你讲。"
        },
        {
          "character": "姜维",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "老大王有何金言，马上请讲。"
        },
        {
          "character": "迷当",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "叫你下马，难道孤还有什么歹意之处？"
        },
        {
          "character": "姜维",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "看老大王变脸变色，待我下马。"
        },
        {
          "character": "迷当",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "看枪。"
        },
        {
          "character": "姜维",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "老大王，为何提枪就刺？"
        },
        {
          "character": "迷当",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "这兵将人马，本是孤家的，借与不借，全凭孤家。你为何再背地辱骂孤家？"
        },
        {
          "character": "姜维",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "此话是何人讲的？"
        },
        {
          "character": "迷当",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "此乃是陈泰讲的，难道还是假的不成嘛！"
        },
        {
          "character": "姜维",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "老大王，有道是旁耳之言，不可深信。"
        },
        {
          "character": "迷当",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "什么旁耳之言，你看枪吧！"
        },
        {
          "character": "姜维",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "老大王再三逼迫，姜维无礼了。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（姜维、迷当同开打，同下。）"
        }
      ],
